{"tid":1462084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"817一齊再入機場   唔搞紅土","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:28:00.000Z","uid":239663,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"991575ee52399f9605b7ce6a2310d9338c5f508c","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"我係打工仔<br />\n<br />\n琴日都係射波去機場, 但係今日做番個打工仔<br />\n我相信好多人都係咁, 因為大家都好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n但今日就得學生入機場, 用人數做癱瘓係好難<br />\n估計未來嗰幾日人數都唔會多到可以星期一咁, 如果次次都要用不合作令機場癱瘓, 只會令香港人同遊客甚至手足反感同爭執<br />\n<br />\n所以希望各位嚟緊幾日入機場唔夠人嘅就做番普通宣傳先, 如果大家有共識唔會阻遊客但係有撚屌係要阻, 就一齊阻止佢唔好做傻事啦<br />\n<br />\n假如平日放工多人可以癱瘓機場當然好, 唔得就等星期六<br />\n之後818再集氣上街輪林鄭中出大波驊   還眼<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b003cb75e25bf3a502bded8f723130c38d53d1","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8735453b1c2e3260752e3953469eec45cdd956bb","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"16739ab38ac664227086340ca8613ff275f7e07c","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"0ff1e0585d140f06d73556acb0e7f2a70e2fe960","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"e8faf6e24188070a8e6741a428755e477837be46","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"841ac33b01626526afaa92c1010e0a2804411288","tid":1462084,"uid":239663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"448ebd09479cd9ae9c26a05187f815fe294cb5ec","tid":1462084,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"